title: Moving back to Hebb
description: The construction on the Hebb Building is nearly complete and we have already started moving items into the new Fizz penthouse in Hebb. The penthouse will be available for use at the start of next semester, to ensure you have access to the new space fill out this Google form.

title: E-Week Coming Soon
description: It's almost time for E-Week, the most exciting week of the year. Help us secure Fizz victory for a second year in a row! See here for a description of all the E-Week events and sign up for tryouts here. Hope to see you all there.

title: Happy Holidays
description: As this semester draws to a close, the Fizz Council would like to wish you all a wonderful break. You've worked hard and you've earned it. We'll see you in 2020 with more events, advice and messages.
